<h1>Goal Check-in: <%= @goal.title %></h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p>It's time for a quick check-in on your goal. How's it going?</p>

<% if @goal.progress.present? && @goal.progress > 0 %>
<p><strong>Current Progress:</strong> <%= @goal.progress %>%</p>
<% end %>

<% if @goal.due_date.present? %>
<p><strong>Due Date:</strong> <%= @goal.due_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
<% end %>

<p>Take a moment to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Update your progress</li>
  <li>Review what's working</li>
  <li>Identify any blockers</li>
  <li>Adjust your approach if needed</li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= @app_url %>" class="button">View Goal</a>
</p>

<p>Keep up the great work!</p>
